snippet.title: Jubilee | Digital Release & Deluxe Edition | PlayStation 5
snippet.description:
Head over to redartgames.com to preorder your Deluxe Edition of Jubilee and get exclusive bonuses: a poster and a sheet of stickers! This game won't be available anywhere else, so don't be late!

Jubilee is coming digitally to Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, PS4|5 and Nintendo Switch on February 9th!

Jubilee is about pure precision platforming. Jump and spin through a variety of challenges: no upgrades, no power-ups. Collect gems and rescue animals. There's multiple routes through the diverse regions of the world: make your own way to the exit... and freedom!

- Enjoy precision platforming in a non-linear world!
- Save the animals by completing challenges and collect gems to show your skills!
- Come back to the game with a second unlockable character and many secrets to uncover!
- Speedrunning options for those who can't get enough of the challenge!

#jubilee #platformer #platforming #precisionplatforming #collectathon #finalbossblues #redartgames #playstation5 #xbox #nintend
